    "ideation": "The newspaper emoji is performed as an 'intense investigator' or 'voracious reader.' The animation mimics the rapid saccadic eye movements of someone scanning columns of text—snapping left to right across narrow fields. The emotional arc moves from systematic scanning to a sudden 'scoop' discovery. The mouth acts as the printing press: starting as a flat, serious line, then turning into a rolling, high-frequency wave to simulate the mechanical hum and jitter of a high-speed press. Color begins in newsprint grayscale and shifts to a celebratory yellow-gold when the headline is finally found.",
